welcome_message_title: Welcome to San Jose del Monte
welcome_message_body: Welcome to San Jose del Monte, where the lush greenery and vibrant culture await you. Known for its beautiful landscapes and friendly locals, we invite you to explore and immerse yourself in all that our charming city has to offer. Enjoy your stay!

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Baler Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Baler Airport handles all freight and logistics operations.

wifi.note: Free wifi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Terminal 1
terminals.description: The oldest and largest terminal at Ninoy Aquino International Airport, serving both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal 2
terminals.description: Also known as the Centennial Terminal, it serves as the primary hub for Philippine Airlines.

terminals.name: Terminal 3
terminals.description: The newest and largest terminal at Ninoy Aquino International Airport, serving both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal 4
terminals.description: The smallest terminal at Ninoy Aquino International Airport, serving mainly domestic flights.

wifi.note: Passengers can enjoy free WiFi access for up to 2 hours.
